abstract: SA2 based data for Selected Person Characteristics by Sex, Basic Community Profile Table B01, for 2011 Census. Count of all persons on Census night based on place of usual residence. Data sourced from: http://www.abs.gov.au/census. For further information about these and related statistics, contact the National Information and Referral Services on 1300 135 070. Periodicity: 5-Yearly.
